{"tid":167403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《美女與野獸》加斯頓爆紅！　迪士尼考慮開發獨立電影","createTime":"2017-03-22T20:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T08:09:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54c6e5fb3a787722dd953a92b62e58871c962b75","tid":167403,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T20:09:03.000Z","msg":"艾瑪華森（Emma Watson）演出電影《美女與野獸》（Beauty and The Beast）全球上映開出票房紅盤，反派加斯頓及野獸城堡中的燭台、時鐘甚至比主角還要紅。不過22日傳出電影不會拍攝續集，不過正在考慮開發角色獨立電影的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2403/d2403291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2403%2Fd2403291.jpg&h=18642329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《美女與野獸》反派加斯頓比野獸還紅。（圖／翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒《Deadline》報導，迪士尼影業製作總裁Sean Bailey明確表示《美女與野獸》不會拍攝續集，不過仍會考慮前傳、外傳開發的可能性。雖然沒有透露具體方向，不過片中包括野獸城堡中的僕人、加斯頓和來富等都有開發潛力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2398/d2398304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2398%2Fd2398304.jpg&h=d7a9cc19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《美女與野獸》時鐘、燭台、茶壺太太人氣超旺。（圖／迪士尼提供）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，《美女與野獸》動畫版也曾推出《美女與野獸：貝兒的心願》和《美女與野獸：貝兒的奇幻世界》兩部延伸動畫。真人版童話電影也有拍攝延伸電影的例子，像是《公主與狩獵者》就曾拍攝前傳《狩獵者：凜冬之戰》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/890169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F890169&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fe9bb233\" target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/890169</a>"},{"pid":"420c7d022dad98cecb6015c81983cdaa53488d6b","tid":167403,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T20:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hahatai.com/sites/default/files/u1031/500x302x10_4.jpg.pagespeed.ic.8RdR9pVu__.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hahatai.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fu1031%2F500x302x10_4.jpg.pagespeed.ic.8RdR9pVu__.webp&h=9f4195ae&s={S